00:46:47.938 --> 00:46:49.206
President Obama: Oh, wow!

00:46:49.206 --> 00:46:50.274
(laughter)

00:46:50.274 --> 00:46:51.375
Well, you're just
putting Sam's business

00:46:51.375 --> 00:46:52.242
all out there.

00:46:52.242 --> 00:46:54.278
(laughter)

00:46:54.278 --> 00:46:54.745
All right.

00:46:54.745 --> 00:46:55.412
What's your name?

00:46:55.412 --> 00:46:56.680
Female Speaker:
Lisandra Rickards.

00:46:56.680 --> 00:46:59.082
I work for the Branson
